00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:52,960
Life or death,

294
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:54,580
it depends on the fate.

295
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:58,480
No.

296
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,560
I disagree.

297
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:02,400
Mr. Gu.

298
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:06,340
Douwei Club has operated more than

299
00:19:06,340 --> 00:19:07,800
twenty years in Shunyuan.

300
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:09,680
You are neither the first one

301
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,880
nor the last one

302
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,240
to harry me.

303
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:16,320
