304
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:17,600
one after another.

305
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,720
But my club survives

306
00:19:20,800 --> 00:19:22,040
due to my rules.

307
00:19:22,560 --> 00:19:24,520
The rules are the essence of the Mu Family.

308
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:26,160
If no one had obeyed the rules,

309
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,040
like Huang,

310
00:19:27,760 --> 00:19:29,600
who regretted and intended to leave,

311
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:32,080
my club couldn,t have been operated.

312
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:35,400
Even if you hadn,t sealed my club,

313
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,890
it could have been closed on my own.

314
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,140
Gu Yanzhen.

315
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:41,300
Gu Yanzhen.

316
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,160
Mr. Mu.

317
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:49,480
It,s my fault.

318
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:53,250
I am willing to fight for the life-and-death boxing.

319
00:19:56,340 --> 00:19:57,870
You saved my brother and me.

320
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,300
I won,t bring you any trouble.

321
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,360
I just hope if I were alive

322
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:06,400
by a fluke after the fight,

323
00:20:08,100 --> 00:20:09,300
you could release me.

324
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:16,880
Of course.

325
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,880
Life-and-death boxing?

326
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:28,050
To sign the death contract?

327
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:29,260
Gu Yanzhen.

328
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:29,880
Are you mad?

329
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:30,610
Is it signed?

330
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,160
I disagree.

331
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:33,580
But he promised it.

332
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:35,820
I said so much to persuade him.

333
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:36,640
But he…

334
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:38,430
He refused and promised

335
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,740
to fight for the life-and-death boxing.

336
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:43,400
Song!

337
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:44,490
You are so silly.

338
00:20:45,080 --> 00:20:46,640
Mr. Mu is not a good person

339
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:48,170
whose business is so dirty.

340
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:49,920
An evil person fears someone even more evil.

341
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:52,340
You should hand it over to Gu Yanzhen to deal with.

342
00:20:52,340 --> 00:20:53,740
Why did you interfere it?

343
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,330
What do you mean?

344
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,370
I am the evil person?

345
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:01,520
Is the date fixed?

346
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:04,370
The sixth day of next month.

347
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:08,740
Huang Song.

348
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,600
Are you sure about it?

349
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,490
If you hand it over to me,

350
00:21:12,760 --> 00:21:13,840
Mr. Mu dares not

351
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:16,970
to hurt you for fear of offending the Shen Family.

352
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:20,100
Do you mean our family has no honor?

353
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:23,200
Does your family have any honors?

354
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:25,880
Song.

355
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:27,870
You should do as we told you.

356
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:29,880
Fighters of the life-and-death boxing are all outlaws.

357
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:31,540
You have your friends, family

358
00:21:31,560 --> 00:21:33,020
and a bright future ahead.

359
00:21:33,040 --> 00:21:34,340
Why do you take the risk?

360
00:21:34,340 --> 00:21:35,000
Yeah.

361
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,140
Liangchen.

362
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:44,840
I know you are kind to me.

363
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:47,080
But I made the trouble.

364
00:21:47,560 --> 00:21:49,000
When He was in the jail,

365
00:21:49,480 --> 00:21:51,400
I begged Mr. Mu for help

366
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:54,000
and he lent me money without hesitance.

367
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:57,100
No matter what his intention was,

368
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,400
I owed him a favor.

369
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:01,400
So,

370
00:22:02,280 --> 00:22:04,400
I don,t allow you to threaten him.

371
00:22:05,600 --> 00:22:06,800
I will end it

372
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,660
through my own efforts

373
00:22:09,520 --> 00:22:11,800
to requite his kindness.

374
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,600
Don,t worry.

375
00:22:25,560 --> 00:22:26,880
The life-and-death boxing

376
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,320
is just a bluff.

377
00:22:28,560 --> 00:22:30,160
In fact, it,s not a big deal.

378
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,640
You just said that

379
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:36,640
most fighters of the life-and-death boxing are outlaws.

380
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,640
Senior boxers won,t fight for this.

381
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:40,840
I have been in club for a long time

382
00:22:40,840 --> 00:22:42,560
