The levels of fighters

384
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:45,000
are not good.

385
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:50,000
Even in regular matches, my victories are much more than defeats.

386
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:52,040
Not to mention these amateurs.

387
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:53,370
Don,t worry.

388
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:54,160
You can rest assured.

389
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,290
I will surely win it.

390
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,800
Liangchen. Don,t worry.

391
00:22:58,340 --> 00:22:59,200
You decided it?

392
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:01,960
Now that you decided it,

393
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:03,420
