394
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,320
In the remaining twenty days,

395
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:07,560
I won,t fight.

396
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:08,980
I will take a good rest.

397
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,320
To rest is not enough.

398
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:12,320
I,ll find you a boxer

399
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,530
and train yourself.

400
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:16,480
Right.

401
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,240
As matters stand,

402
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:20,560
you should recover your state to the best.

403
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,120
Well.

404
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:24,120
I,ll draw up a training plan for you.

405
00:23:24,640 --> 00:23:25,520
Train yourself

406
00:23:25,840 --> 00:23:27,040
according to my plan.

407
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:30,280
I,m sure all your rivals would be defeated.

408
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:31,000
Right.

409
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:33,600
You should be defensive besides endurance

410
00:23:33,600 --> 00:23:34,260
and skills.

411
00:23:35,080 --> 00:23:37,000
I know several martial masters.

412
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:39,320
I,ll invite them to hit you every day

413
00:23:39,320 --> 00:23:41,000
to build up your defensibility.

414
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,000
So that you won,t even fight

415
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,240
and just exhaust them

416
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:44,200
by bearing their blows.

417
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:44,840
Believe it?

418
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:45,400
Yeah.

419
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:48,040
We will train you as Sergeant Lv did.

420
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:50,080
I believe five coaches of us

421
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:52,010
