436
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,330
You,re welcome.

437
00:26:25,520 --> 00:26:26,180
Liangchen.

438
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:29,200
Shen Junshan.

439
00:26:30,320 --> 00:26:31,040
What,s up?

440
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:32,680
I need to go out now.

441
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,460
Help me to request a leave.

442
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:35,130
Alright.

443
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:37,010
Where are you going?

444
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:39,100
To find Xie Xiang.

445
00:26:40,760 --> 00:26:41,440
Who?

446
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:42,360
Xie Xiang.

447
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:44,720
It,s rare to be free today.

448
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:45,780
I want to visit her.

449
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:48,040
She...

450
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,480
She may not be free.

451
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:53,320
Have you met her?

452
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,320
No. No.

453
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:54,960
No.

454
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:57,100
How do you know she is not free?

455
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:59,240
You know she is always busy.

456
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:00,480
I guess it.

457
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:01,560
She bustles around,

458
00:27:01,560 --> 00:27:02,760
