459
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:05,100
Do your business.

460
00:27:05,100 --> 00:27:05,830
I,m leaving.

461
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,100
What should I do?

462
00:27:22,600 --> 00:27:23,200
Hurry up.

463
00:27:24,280 --> 00:27:24,840
Hurry up.

464
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:34,560
Thank you.

465
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:35,200
Not at all.

466
00:27:58,240 --> 00:27:58,840
Xie Xiang.

467
00:27:59,440 --> 00:28:00,080
Mr. Shen.

468
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,020
What are you doing?

469
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,770
I,m waiting for the car.

470
00:28:06,080 --> 00:28:07,340
Where are you heading?

471
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,340
The bookstore.

472
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:10,170
I wanna go to the bookstore.

473
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:11,400
Get in the car.

474
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:12,260
I,ll drive you.

475
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:13,720
No. Thank you.

476
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:14,840
It doesn,t matter.

477
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:15,440
Get on.

478
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:18,640
Alright.

479
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,940
Do you wanna buy books?

480
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:40,890
I wanna look around.

481
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,330
You can go later.

482
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:48,570
