483
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:50,400
Tulip Dance Troupe from Russia.

484
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,810
They can dance Giselle.

485
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:53,000
Do you wanna watch it?

486
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:53,520
Really?

487
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,210
I know you would like it.

488
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,000
