489
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,370
Do we come too early?

490
00:29:23,080 --> 00:29:23,560
Please.

491
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:02,440
How about it?

492
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,100
Was it good?

493
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:04,260
Brilliant.

494
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:05,730
That,s good.

495
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:10,730
