523
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:48,200
If you were exposed,

524
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,920
no one could save you.

525
00:33:50,360 --> 00:33:51,040
I know it.

526
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:52,850
I,ll send those away tomorrow.

527
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,940
You,d better do it.

528
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:57,480
Is it alright?

529
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,080
OK. OK.

530
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,160
Go.

531
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:02,040
Hurry up.

532
00:34:02,120 --> 00:34:02,680
Don,t push me.

533
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:03,340
Be careful.

534
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:06,040
