00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,400
I heard that he was punished by Guo

586
00:36:57,400 --> 00:36:59,520
for three days in solitary confinement.

587
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:00,450
It was pathetic.

588
00:37:02,480 --> 00:37:02,920
Song!

589
00:37:03,160 --> 00:37:04,690
Why do you look dispirited?

590
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,490
I didn,t sleep well.

591
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,360
You should have a good rest.

592
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,290
It is significant to you tomorrow.

593
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:12,200
Listen to me.

594
00:37:12,200 --> 00:37:12,920
It,s not too late

595
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:14,450
to regret if you are afraid.

596
00:37:14,700 --> 00:37:15,220
No.

597
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,160
I will go.

598
00:37:17,220 --> 00:37:17,950
As your wish.

599
00:37:21,640 --> 00:37:22,370
Don,t worry.

600
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,460
We will go with you tomorrow evening.

601
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:25,680
I will go, too.

602
00:37:26,080 --> 00:37:26,640
No need.

603
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:29,480
It would be a disaster if the Sergeants knew it.

604
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:30,740
But you can,t go alone.

605
00:37:31,220 --> 00:37:31,840
Come.

606
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:33,980
It doesn,t matter.

607
00:37:34,220 --> 00:37:35,480
I can solve it on my own.

608
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:37,000
Take it.

609
00:37:37,680 --> 00:37:39,140
The yolk has been removed.

610
00:37:40,520 --> 00:37:41,200
Thank you.

611
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:52,700
Did you sleep well last night?

612
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,020
It was good.

613
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:57,640
The door was almost smashed.

614
00:37:57,640 --> 00:37:58,370
Are you sure?

615
00:37:58,960 --> 00:38:00,680
It has nothing to do with you.

616
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,040
Get your hands away.

617
00:38:06,040 --> 00:38:06,640
Nope.

618
00:38:08,700 --> 00:38:09,480
Have the meal.

619
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:10,120
Nope.

620
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:13,040
Alright.

621
00:38:13,040 --> 00:38:13,640
So be it.

622
00:38:30,700 --> 00:38:31,160
Xiaoyu.

623
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,160
It,s almost done.

624
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:36,880
Did anyone follow you on the road?

625
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:37,480
No.

626
00:38:37,680 --> 00:38:38,680
We made a fraud.

627
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:40,360
The police surnamed He

628
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,220
still stayed

629
00:38:41,220 --> 00:38:43,020
at Warehouse No.17 with his men.

630
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:45,720
Get prepared.

631
00:38:46,220 --> 00:38:48,220
Mr. Zhou will pick up the goods tomorrow.

632
00:38:48,220 --> 00:38:48,880
It,s fine. Xiaoyu.

633
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:49,440
I know it.

634
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:51,440
Xiaoyu.

635
00:38:52,200 --> 00:38:53,730
All are light machine guns.

636
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,250
All are made in Britain.

637
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:56,650
No wonder

638
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:58,960
the police are so crazy for them.

639
00:39:00,640 --> 00:39:01,640
It is worthy for us

640
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,520
to take such great risks.

641
00:39:05,220 --> 00:39:06,440
Stay here tonight.

642
00:39:07,200 --> 00:39:08,120
Keep vigilant.

643
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:09,560
Don,t make any mistake.

644
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:10,420
Get it. Xiaoyu.

645
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:11,880
Leave.

646
00:39:12,040 --> 00:39:12,520
Go.

647
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:15,850
We,re leaving, Xiaoyu.

648
00:40:11,960 --> 00:40:12,890
What do you want?

649
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:14,170
Pretend to be a hero?

650
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:15,220
Face your enemy alone?

651
00:40:15,220 --> 00:40:16,920
You want to have fun alone.

652
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,980
Don,t you see us as your brothers?

653
00:40:19,220 --> 00:40:19,880
Huang Song.

654
00:40:20,080 --> 00:40:20,700
I warn you.

655
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:23,920
I,ve bet you all my money for meals this month.

656
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:24,980
If you dare to lose,

657
00:40:25,220 --> 00:40:26,880
you wash my underwear for a month.

658
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:28,810
Don,t you only have one underwear?

659
00:40:29,080 --> 00:40:30,220
Do you think I have only one as you do?

660
00:40:30,220 --> 00:40:31,150
Have you seen it?

661
00:40:31,700 --> 00:40:32,200
Song.

662
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:33,660
We will go with you.

663
00:40:37,520 --> 00:40:38,240
Thank you.

664
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:40,220
Thank you.

665
00:40:40,700 --> 00:40:41,630
Don,t be afraid.

666
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,700
If the rival is powerful,

667
00:40:43,700 --> 00:40:44,630
we will help you.

668
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:46,250
Don,t worry.

669
00:41:17,880 --> 00:41:18,400
Song.

670
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:19,720
Song.

671
00:41:20,200 --> 00:41:20,840
Mr. Mu said it.

672
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,220
Go to see him at the lounge.

673
00:41:22,220 --> 00:41:23,920
Did he say what the matter is?

674
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:24,480
Nope.

675
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,940
Go to visit him now.

676
00:41:27,080 --> 00:41:28,160
I,ll go to visit him.

677
00:41:28,160 --> 00:41:29,220
Let,s go together.

678
00:41:38,680 --> 00:41:39,740
Where is your boss?

679
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:42,960
Song.

680
00:41:48,220 --> 00:41:49,220
Where is the boss?

681
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,560
He was here just now.

682
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:51,160
But

683
00:41:51,480 --> 00:41:52,740
two Russians came here

684
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:53,920
and took him away.

685
00:41:54,700 --> 00:41:55,440
Russians?

686
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:59,020
Do you know whom I will fight with?

687
00:41:59,080 --> 00:41:59,640
Peng Jiu.

688
00:42:01,700 --> 00:42:02,600
Who is Peng Jiu?

689
00:42:02,700 --> 00:42:03,560
Is he powerful?

690
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:08,400
Didn,t Peng Jiu hurt his leg?

691
00:42:08,640 --> 00:42:09,680
Can he fight?

692
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:11,000
He is lame.

693
00:42:11,220 --> 00:42:13,080
He can,t fight in normal matches.

694
00:42:13,680 --> 00:42:16,280
So he gambles it on the life-and-death boxing.

695
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:17,080
Hey, Song.

696
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:19,000
You know it,s him.

697
00:42:19,200 --> 00:42:20,800
You should be reassured now.

698
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:22,170
In the match,

699
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,880
you don,t need to fight him at all.

700
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:25,280
Just run around the stage

701
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:26,960
and exhaust him to death.

702
00:42:28,680 --> 00:42:30,080
How could it be like this?

703
00:42:30,220 --> 00:42:32,880
Let me fight a lame chain smoker?

704
00:42:33,700 --> 00:42:34,880
I can,t do that.

705
00:42:37,220 --> 00:42:37,840
Song.

706
00:42:38,160 --> 00:42:38,700
This is

707
00:42:38,700 --> 00:42:39,700
your final match.

708
00:42:40,040 --> 00:42:41,700
The boss neither wants to break the rules,

709
00:42:41,700 --> 00:42:42,960
nor to embarrass you.

710
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:46,700
It is said that even Mr. Gu in Gu Mansion intervened.

711
00:42:46,700 --> 00:42:48,640
So the boss must show some respect.

712
00:42:50,220 --> 00:42:50,880
Song.

713
00:42:51,360 --> 00:42:53,160
You know such an eminent person.

714
00:42:53,400 --> 00:42:54,480
If you become famous someday,

715
00:42:54,480 --> 00:42:56,400
don,t forget to promote me.

716
00:43:01,680 --> 00:43:02,810
Where are you going?

717
00:43:03,200 --> 00:43:06,040
I will bet all my savings on Song.

718
00:43:06,220 --> 00:43:07,360
This is a rare opportunity

719
00:43:07,360 --> 00:43:08,560
to make a big fortune.

720
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:11,480
Ji Jin.

721
00:43:11,840 --> 00:43:12,640
That,s right!

722
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:13,600
Wait for me!
